PN,43701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FA man accused of causing his wife to
OL,7,Ftake her own life by abusing her has
OL,8,Fdenied using a belt to choke her
OL,9,Fduring sex and said she would ask him
OL,10,Fto choke her.
OL,12,FChristopher Trybus, from Swindon, is
OL,13,Faccused of the manslaughter of Tarryn
OL,14,FBaird, who took her own life in
OL,15,FNovember 2017 aged 34.
OL,17,FThe 43-year-old also faces charges at
OL,18,FWinchester Crown Court of controlling
OL,19,Fand coercive behaviour and two charges
OL,20,Fof rape.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
