FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FThe coercive control charge alleges
OL,7,FTrybus controlled Ms Baird through
OL,8,Fusing and threatening violence towards
OL,9,Fher, sexually assaulting her,
OL,10,Fmonitoring her whereabouts, limiting
OL,11,Faccess to finance, threatening to
OL,12,Freveal private information to her
OL,13,Ffamily and isolating her from her
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FThe jury was played an audio clip
OL,17,Frecorded by Ms Baird engaged in what
OL,18,Fthe defendant described as "foreplay"
OL,19,Fwith him which was discovered by her
OL,20,Fmother after her death.
OL,26,@zD@\OUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
