PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FHe has told the court he had bought a
OL,7,Fkit from Amazon which included cuffs,
OL,8,Frope, neck collar with leash, ball
OL,9,Fgag, a whip and blindfold.
OL,11,FTrybus said the audio clip started
OL,12,Fwith him saying: "What's going on
OL,13,Fthere love?" and during the recording
OL,14,FMs Baird can be heard to be grunting
OL,15,Fand gasping loudly.
OL,17,FHe said: "The sense of it wasn't
OL,18,Funusual, not all the times it was like
OL,19,Fthat, it wasn't unusual, not all the
OL,20,Ftime was it like that."
OL,26,@tD@ROUuD@LO]yD@JOU|D@WO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
