PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus continued: "It may be in this
OL,7,Finstant a bit more unusual but at the
OL,8,Ftime it didn't seem unusual to me, but
OL,9,Fmaybe put on a bit."
OL,11,FThe defendant added: "We always joked
OL,12,Fwe had a safe word, maybe it came from
OL,13,Fa movie, the safe word was
OL,14,F'pineapple', she never used it, maybe
OL,15,Fout and about, joking about it."
OL,17,FHe said that slapping noises would
OL,18,Fhave been him "spanking her on the
OL,19,Fbum" with his hand, which he said was
OL,20,F"an aspect of what we did".
OL,26,@nD@SOUqD@TO]sD@VOUwD@`O]zD@OOU{D@DO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
