PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus told the court he said at one
OL,7,Fpoint: "Where are those handcuffs?"
OL,8,Fand added: "She was struggling and I
OL,9,Fwant to do something else, progress to
OL,10,Fsex, there isn't usually a lot of
OL,11,Fforeplay."
OL,13,FHe said he did not think the noises
OL,14,Fmade by Ms Baird were from pain, and
OL,15,Fadded: "I guess if she said 'that
OL,16,Fhurts' or something, I would have
OL,17,Fstopped. I do not think it was pain."
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@cO]pD@LOUsD@JO]wD@HOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
