PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FThe court has heard Ms Baird had
OL,7,Falleged Trybus had used a belt around
OL,8,Fher neck, which he denied but said he
OL,9,Fhad used his hands because "she wanted
OL,10,Fme to choke her", although he had not
OL,11,Fused pressure to hurt or cause her to
OL,12,Flose consciousness.
OL,14,FThe trial has also heard Ms Baird told
OL,15,Fmedical professionals she had fainted
OL,16,Fafter sex, and Trybus said he was
OL,17,Faware on one occasion when she had
OL,18,Ffainted on the landing and another in
OL,19,Fthe shower.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
