FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus said he had not believed at the
OL,7,Ftime that Ms Baird had been
OL,8,F"struggling" with drinking and had
OL,9,Ffelt mental health issues and PTSD `
OL,10,Fwhich the court has heard was from
OL,11,Fwitnessing violent robberies in South
OL,12,FAfrica where they grew up ` were the
OL,13,F"root cause" of her problems.
OL,15,FHe said: "It sounds horrible, maybe I
OL,16,Fdidn't believe she really had any
OL,17,Fissues and maybe she did, I wouldn't
OL,18,Fsay that to her, I would just try to
OL,19,Fhelp her."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]uD@AOUuD@LO]wD@JOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
