PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus said he tried to dissuade Ms
OL,7,FBaird from buying prescription
OL,8,Fmedication online and said: "Firstly I
OL,9,Fsaid to her 'You do not know what is
OL,10,Fin this stuff, it's not coming from
OL,11,FBoots, it's coming from god knows
OL,12,Fwhere, if you need it your doctor will
OL,13,Fprescribe it to you, don't do that'."
OL,15,FThe defendant said they used an app to
OL,16,Ftrack each other's phones and added:
OL,17,F"It was much easier for her to track
OL,18,Fme and also with her fainting it was
OL,19,Fnice to know where she was if need be."
OL,26,@pD@]OUuD@eO]yD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
