PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FThe court has heard Ms Baird had
OL,7,Freported to medical professionals
OL,8,Frepeatedly suffering injuries.
OL,10,FHe said she had told him various
OL,11,Freasons for the injuries, such as she
OL,12,Fhad "slipped down the stairs" or in
OL,13,Fthe bath, and she had said she
OL,14,F"bruised easily".
OL,16,FTrybus said she also suffered a "few
OL,17,Fbumps and bruises" from boxing classes
OL,18,Fshe attended, and she also had
OL,19,Fbruising from using a foam roller to
OL,20,Fmassage her muscles after going to the
OL,21,Fgym.
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@]O]vD@AOUvD@PO]xD@aOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
