OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus denied that he had assaulted Ms
OL,7,FBaird with a metal pole in November
OL,8,F2016 and said that he was abroad
OL,9,Fworking in Gothenburg, Sweden, and
OL,10,Fthen in Amsterdam, Netherlands, on the
OL,11,Falleged date and in total between
OL,12,FNovember 8 and 23.
OL,14,FThe court heard that Ms Baird had
OL,15,Fclaimed that at this time she had left
OL,16,Ftheir home and was staying in a hotel
OL,17,Fwhere the defendant had managed to
OL,18,Ftrack her and she went back home with
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
