OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774786269
OL,3,CMan accused of causing wife's suicide
OL,4,Cdenies choking her with belt
OL,6,FTrybus said that his work at both
OL,7,Foverseas locations were "stressful
OL,8,Ftimes" and "long hours" as he
OL,9,Finstalled new business computer
OL,10,Fsystems.
OL,12,FHe said that if he had not been at
OL,13,Fwork during that time "everyone would
OL,14,Fhave been 'where the hell is Chris',
OL,15,Fwould they be able to continue? I do
OL,16,Fnot think so, they might have had to
OL,17,Fpostpone."
OL,19,FTrybus, a software consultant, denies
OL,20,Fthe charges and the trial continues.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@FO]pD@LOUpD@WO]uD@WOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
